data.description: GRAND OPENING! OPEN HOUSE SATURDAY APRIL 13TH & SUNDAY APRIL 14TH FROM 12:00PM-4:00PM! Welcome home to 624 Santa Rose Hills located in the master planned community of Suntrace and zoned to Katy ISD! Indulge in the epitome of luxury living with this spacious single-story boasting 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and a flexible retreat space. Entertain effortlessly in the wide-open great room featuring a chef's granite kitchen with 42" shaker-style cabinets and a unique T-shaped island. Retreat to the private owner's suite with a spa-like bath offering direct utility access for added convenience. Enjoy modern conveniences like stainless steel appliances, upgraded wood tile flooring, security system, and a sprinkler system. Step outside to your covered outdoor living space and fully sodded yard, completing your picture-perfect oasis. Sunterra residents will have plenty of opportunities for fun, with two world-class amenity complexes – The Retreat Lazy River village and Sol Club Lagoon Village.
